  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/1fe62a23500811aad435301823f13305.poster.avif?t=1614252746\" width=644 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/1fe62a23500811aad435301823f13305.webm?t=1614252746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/1fe62a23500811aad435301823f13305.mp4?t=1614252746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>台南的在地推廣IP  《府城少女力爭上游》 由可洛洛遊戲製作<br>首次的視覺小說遊戲化!!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/041d5a2338ac1beeca9fbdfd31785a80.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——「那個秋石...千萬不可以在台南跟糖分起爭議喔!」</h2>◆由「嗓音不甜也有春天」為遊戲進行全中文配音<br>◇全新原創劇情的視覺小說<br>◆台南市區街景的全新繪製背景<br>◇首次躍上遊戲平台的府城少女們原創故事<br>◆日津樹伶老師擔當主視覺與CG<br>◇一段跨過海洋的與時代的小小愛情<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/4f3548f68e56d0c8b35f8e7671890c56.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ——「這難道是...爺爺的初戀情人嗎?」  </h2>一張泛黃的照片   一封從未寄出的情書<br>青年為了幫助親人尋找過去記憶踏上了台南府城<br>在南臺灣豔陽下與超甜手搖杯的城市中，他將與府城的少女們遭遇怎樣的邂逅呢?<br><br>一段尋找過去的旅程就此展開....<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/00a188d5961e7bff0af4ef0415dd0066.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——『要是活著還要假裝自己，不覺得有點太辛苦了嗎。』</h2>府城第一的美少女(自稱)嚮導，小滿<br>巧遇了來到台南的日本青年秋石，在小滿的帶領下秋石將會找到屬於爺爺過去的記憶嗎?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/3fb9f59aec182f65ef9b742cd07e63db.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——『如果要讓人相信你就不要只是嘴上說說，和剛才一樣用行動來表示吧。』</h2>武廟出身的單純少女，子月<br>性格樂天但有橫衝直撞，對於初到日本的秋石卻抱持著明顯的敵意?<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/63dbf9a1ceec9ce16cddfa7c82854c88.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——『天下可沒有白吃的午餐，禮尚往來是合情合理的事情。』</h2>年輕的關子嶺溫泉旅館當家，小楓<br>出手相助小滿跟秋石的大氣少女，但她要求幫忙的回報會是什麼呢?<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/94eb3802624db8932ebbb2fe25c0b1a5.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各地重新繪製的台南市區景點，等待你重新認識台南——</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/dfdc749456fd3e59bb757445f6c0f192.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=270 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/9812a544a5d9a2e3ef4d3a8b2463cfc6.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=270 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1429610/extras/2c07225259979ae1fc88df3e252f5195.avif?t=1614252746\" width=630 height=270 /></span>",
